---
title: Turkish Spiced Chicken with Almond Rice, Roasted Sweet Potato and Garlic-Lemon Yogurt Sauce
description: The star of this dish is the warm Turkish spice blend that seasons our tender chicken. It's drizzled with a garlic-lemon yogurt sauce and served alongside fragrant almond rice for a meal that will transport your tastebuds to Istanbul.
